        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "Thanks for joining the ad-hoc. Product agrees the pattern is worth tackling, but they want a crisp scope before assigning writers. Today we need to define what the reusable template actually contains and which regional needs must appear on day one."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "lucas",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "From EMEA, the template needs three sections at minimum: in-region data handling, rollout scope boundaries, and multilingual training assumptions. Those are the parts I keep rewriting for Corso and Istanbul."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "sophia",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "AMER needs a compliance evidence section with control mappings, incident-notification language, and tenant-isolation examples. If we have those pre-approved, MetroPharma-style reviews get dramatically faster."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "meilin",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "APAC needs the same core content, plus a localization lens. The template should make it easy to explain what is standard versus what requires local adaptation, especially for Japanese operating teams."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "mat",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "That sounds like one document with reusable modules rather than three separate documents. If product builds a base template and we add regional appendices, we can serve global consistency without losing local relevance."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "lucas",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "Exactly. Corso does not need the whole global story, but it does need confidence that our base answer is repeatable and governance-backed."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "sophia",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "And MetroPharma would benefit from knowing the same response framework works in other regulated contexts, even if we never name the other customers."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "User": "mat",
        "Task": "Speak",
        "Assignments": [
          {
            "ParameterName": "text_to_speech",
            "ParameterValue": "Perfect. Facilitator, summarize the scope definition as a reusable compliance-and-localization template with core modules plus regional appendices. That summary is what I will take into next Wednesday's director sync."
          }
        ]
      },
